# This directory is an AGILE BOARD: every `…/$defs:task` file in it is a card, grouped into
# columns by the `dev` workflow's states (backlog → ready → in-progress → done/cancelled).
# Dragging a card to another column rewrites that task's state annotation (re-tags it). The
# states come from the PROJECT-GLOBAL `dev` workflow (the root `tags/` taxonomy) that the cards
# also point at — one source of truth, no per-board copy. Spec: ../../TICKETS.md §3.
!!<*yamlover:$defs:board>
workflow: *::yamlover:tags:workflow:dev
